member.param:
Array of objects which contain items of same type. Every item should have a match with data assigned to the DataSource of ComboWrapper/ComboModel.

            Examples:

            new object[] { 13, 3.5, -15 }

            new object[] { "item2", "item3" }

            new object[] { new DateTime(2011, 8, 28), new DateTime(2011, 8, 29) }

Array of selected indexes. Indexes should be positive values and not larger than number of records assigned to the DataSource of ComboWrapper/ComboModel.

            Example:

            new int[] { 2, 5 }

